  "3015950": {
    "name": "Kun’tewiktuk: A Mi’kmaw Adventure",
    "steam_appid": 3015950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/fceb698667c74a582156cf12210d44e3.avif?t=1742618799\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras_big/fceb698667c74a582156cf12210d44e3.avif?t=1742618799 width=800 height=395 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/decd271887856189cd8f277bac204508.avif?t=1742618799\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras_big/decd271887856189cd8f277bac204508.avif?t=1742618799 width=800 height=177 /></span><strong>Kun’tewiktuk: A Mi’kmaw Adventure</strong> is a fantasy adventure game inspired by Mi’kmaw legend and folklore.  It takes place in Unama'ki (&quot;Land of the Fog&quot;), which is known today as Cape Breton Island, Canada. It chronicles the adventures of two young siblings <strong>Wasuek</strong> (&quot;Flower&quot;) and her brother <strong>U'n</strong> (&quot;Fog&quot;).  The siblings get separated one summer morning and they go on an adventure through the spirit world to reunite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/f9990511a17a550b33ea96d50ee4dc15.poster.avif?t=1742618799\" width=630 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/f9990511a17a550b33ea96d50ee4dc15.webm?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/f9990511a17a550b33ea96d50ee4dc15.mp4?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/23619739036f4be0400193f5efc9de3c.avif?t=1742618799\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras_big/23619739036f4be0400193f5efc9de3c.avif?t=1742618799 width=800 height=177 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our game's genre is best described as a <strong>fantasy adventure</strong>.  It’s played in <strong>third-person perspective</strong>, and the player has access to a menu system that allows them to assign and switch weapons and abilities as they become available through the gameplay.  The gameplay will sometimes weave back into the natural world, depending on the objective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our young adventurers will be granted special abilities as they progress through the game.  These special abilities are drawn from nature and become available through the completion of assignments and quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/48873a128e2326b2c42e02751591e16e.poster.avif?t=1742618799\" width=630 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/48873a128e2326b2c42e02751591e16e.webm?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/48873a128e2326b2c42e02751591e16e.mp4?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kun'tewiktuk (pr. &quot;gon-dew-ik-duk&quot;)</strong> is the Mi'kmaw word for &quot;the place of the rock&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Mi'kmaq (pr. &quot;meeg-ah-mah&quot;)</strong> are indigenous peoples who are among the original inhabitants in the Atlantic Provinces of Canada. Oral history and archeological evidence place the Mi’kmaq in the region for more than 10,000 years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay alternates between our two young heroes as the story progresses from one assignment to the next.  As the story begins, Wasuek is working her way to U’n.  U’n eventually escapes his captor and begins working his way home, pursued by the spirit-eating creature.  They continue working their way toward each other with the goal of reuniting and making their way back home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/c80a30216f8f7471d4e165b7f8c683eb.avif?t=1742618799\" width=800 height=92 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wasuek</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pronounced &quot;wuz-a-wek&quot;, it means &quot;flower&quot; in Mi'kmaw.  Wasuek is brave, intelligent, and determined.  She cares for her family, community, and her brother, and is fiercely protective of them. When she puts her mind to something, get out of her way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/7d30d69db768eb1c18925be3c7acd7e5.poster.avif?t=1742618799\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/7d30d69db768eb1c18925be3c7acd7e5.webm?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/7d30d69db768eb1c18925be3c7acd7e5.mp4?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>U'n</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pronounced &quot;oon&quot;, it means &quot;fog&quot; in Mi'kmaw.  U'n is brave and adventurous like his sister, and can sometimes wander off in exploration without thinking of the consequences.  He's strong, energetic, and never turns down a challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/e89a1e0610e494a2918fc54df203d150.poster.avif?t=1742618799\" width=630 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/e89a1e0610e494a2918fc54df203d150.webm?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/e89a1e0610e494a2918fc54df203d150.mp4?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/9ccecf1b6d00e7992fe6c62d466b0089.avif?t=1742618799\" width=600 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/b12955997d9bb23124530eefe0bd8082.avif?t=1742618799\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras_big/b12955997d9bb23124530eefe0bd8082.avif?t=1742618799 width=800 height=1950 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/682a7ba868d209478bbc821ac8b18e5d.avif?t=1742618799\" width=700 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter a variety of characters from Mi'kmaw legend, including the Great Chief Kluskap, who will guide you on your journey... if you are worthy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/d79fb35ba73ce2083ec0b2122e313740.poster.avif?t=1742618799\" width=630 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/d79fb35ba73ce2083ec0b2122e313740.webm?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/d79fb35ba73ce2083ec0b2122e313740.mp4?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/483a2f86f6237cd76cdc262382abc4d0.avif?t=1742618799\" width=600 height=69 /></span>The game will also feature a series of mini-games, testing the player’s skills in puzzles, memory, and dexterity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/784ee5a26c46faa48099408a05ff54e4.avif?t=1742618799\" width=800 height=457 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/6b6fc2d8c4106f4cf077c4da15d3e013.avif?t=1742618799\" width=600 height=69 /></span>The game's villains and adversaries are inspired by Mi'kmaw legend and folklore.  They include ogres, ice creatures, giant spirit animals, and much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/489fa861bca258c321e4c2e675da1f60.poster.avif?t=1742618799\" width=630 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/489fa861bca258c321e4c2e675da1f60.webm?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/489fa861bca258c321e4c2e675da1f60.mp4?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/c83f675bc5287bb841001a81bd92818c.avif?t=1742618799\" width=600 height=69 /></span>The game offers players a range of gameplay experiences, including both traditional weapons as well as magical abilities.  It also offers different environments, landscapes, and gameplay as both of our young heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/f39afaedd454cd9f847a4226a7098b6b.poster.avif?t=1742618799\" width=630 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/f39afaedd454cd9f847a4226a7098b6b.webm?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/f39afaedd454cd9f847a4226a7098b6b.mp4?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/9de28e2f2443f9dfa924a287508a0130.avif?t=1742618799\" width=600 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will face boss-level adversaries throughout the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/5af51b52ed1d0f6008bff717b9b19421.poster.avif?t=1742618799\" width=630 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/5af51b52ed1d0f6008bff717b9b19421.webm?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015950/extras/5af51b52ed1d0f6008bff717b9b19421.mp4?t=1742618799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
